udian American|Bermudan]]{{refn|name=WI|group=fn}}\n|370\n|170\n|-\n|[[British West Indies|British West Indian]]{{refn|name=WI|group=fn}}\n|1,858\n|485\n|-\n|[[Dutch West Indian American|Dutch West Indian]]{{refn|name=WI|group=fn}}\n|1,960\n|329\n|-\n|[[Haitian Americans|Haitian]]{{refn|name=WI|group=fn}}\n|7,363\n|1,046\n|-\n|[[Jamaican American|Jamaican]]{{refn|name=WI|group=fn}}\n|28,675\n|1,877\n|-\n|[[Trinidadian and Tobagonian American|Trinidadian and Tobagonian]]{{refn|name=WI|group=fn}}\n|5,357\n|716\n|-\n|[[Virgin Islands American|U.S. Virgin Islander]]{{refn|name=WI|group=fn}}\n|756\n|288\n|-\n|West Indian{{refn|name=WI|group=fn}}\n|9,221\n|1,247\n|-\n|Other West Indian{{refn|name=WI|group=fn}}\n|276\n|124\n|-\n|[[Yugoslav American|Yugoslavian]]\n|33,363\n|1,830\n|-\n|Other groups\n|24,394,120\n|29,987\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\" |Footnotes:<br />{{reflist|group=fn}}\n|}\n{{col-break}}\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\" style=\"font-size: 90%;\"\n|-\n! Ancestry !! 2010 Population<ref>{{cite web |url= http://factfinder.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_SF2_PCT1&prodType=table |archive-url= https://archive.today/20200212211748/http://factfinder.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_SF2_PCT1&prodType=table |url-status= dead |archive-date= 2020-02-12 |title=Total Population |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=2010 |website=[[2010 United States Census|2010 Census]], [[United States Census Bureau]] |publisher=United States Department of Commerce |access-date=May 1, 2013}}</ref> !! Percentage of Total Population\n|-\n|<u>[[Non-Hispanic whites|White, not Hispanic or Latino]]</u>\n|15,763,625\n|42.3%\n|-\n|<u>[[Hispanic and Latino Americans|Hispanic or Latino (of any race)]]</u>\n|14,013,719\n|37.6%\n|-\n|[[Mexican Americans|Mexican]]\n|11,423,146\n|30.6%\n|-\n|[[Salvadoran American|Salvadoran]]\n|573,956\n|1.5%\n|-\n|[[Guatemalan Americans|Guatemalan]]\n|332,737\n|