als]]\n| {{ntsh|2}}Super Bowl Champion ([[Super Bowl XLIV|XLIV]])\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| [[2004 NFL Draft|2004]]\n| align=\"center\"| 7\n| align=\"center\"| 3\n| align=\"center\"| 236\n| align=\"center\"| {{sortname|Rashad|Washington}}\n| align=\"center\"| DB\n| align=\"center\"| [[New York Jets]]\n| align=\"center\"| {{ntsh|0}}\u2014\n|- bgcolor=\"#D0E7FF\"\n| align=\"center\"| [[2005 NFL Draft|2005]]\n| align=\"center\"| 4\n| align=\"center\"| 29\n| align=\"center\"| 130\n| align=\"center\"| {{sortname|Darren|Sproles}}<sup>\u2021</sup>\n| align=\"center\"| RB\n| align=\"center\"| [[San Diego Chargers]]\n| {{ntsh|2}}Super Bowl Champion ([[Super Bowl LII|LII]])<br>Pro Bowl ([[2015 Pro Bowl|2014]], [[2016 Pro Bowl|2015]])\n|- \n| align=\"center\"| [[2006 NFL Draft|2006]]\n| align=\"center\"| 6\n| align=\"center\"| 18\n| align=\"center\"| 187\n| align=\"center\"| {{sortname|Jeromey|Clary}}\n| align=\"center\"| T\n| align=\"center\"| [[San Diego Chargers]]\n| align=\"center\"| {{ntsh|0}}\u2014\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| [[2007 NFL Draft|2007]]\n| align=\"center\"| 3\n| align=\"center\"| 10\n| align=\"center\"| 74\n| align=\"center\"| {{sortname|Yamon|Figurs}}\n| align=\"center\"| WR\n| align=\"center\"| [[Baltimore Ravens]]\n| align=\"center\"| {{ntsh|0}}\u2014\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| [[2007 NFL Draft|2007]]\n| align=\"center\"| 6\n| align=\"center\"| 12\n| align=\"center\"| 186\n| align=\"center\"| {{sortname|Thomas|Clayton|Thomas Clayton (American football)}}\n| align=\"center\"| RB\n| align=\"center\"| [[San Francisco 49ers]]\n| align=\"center\"| {{ntsh|0}}\u2014\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| [[2007 NFL Draft|2007]]\n| align=\"center\"| 7\n| align=\"center\"| 8\n| align=\"center\"| 218\n| align=\"center\"| {{sortname|Zac|Diles}}\n| align=\"center\"| LB\n| align=\"center\"| [[Houston Texans]]\n| align=\"center\"| {{ntsh|0}}\u2014\n|- bgcolor=\"#D0E7FF\"\n| align=\"center\"| [[2008 NFL Draft|2008]]\n| align=\"center\"| 2\n| align=\"center\"| 5\n| align=\"center\"| 36\n| a